{"tid":1067984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年全球生活費最貴排行榜：香港首度排榜首　與巴黎新加坡並列","createTime":"2019-03-19T02:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T02:36:46.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2bf2c5b7053fdde1c59cc72b360378335c675f","tid":1067984,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:24:29.000Z","msg":"英國經濟學人智庫（Economist Intelligence Unit）公佈2019年全球生活成本調查報告，香港、巴黎及新加坡共同成為全球生活費最貴城市，其中香港更加是連跳3位首次居冠。<br />\n<br />\n調查會評估全球133個國家逾150項物品的成本，香港去年排名第四，今年破天荒首度居冠。與香港並列的法國巴黎生活成本一直偏高，自2003年以來佔據全球生活費最高城市十大位置，新加坡則是蟬聯冠軍寶座。<br />\n<br />\n十大生活費最貴城市主要來自亞洲及歐洲大城巿，蘇黎世排行第四，日本的大阪上升6位，與瑞士日內瓦並列第五。紐約和洛杉磯是唯一打入十大的北美城市，其中紐約上升7位，與首爾和哥本哈根並排第七；洛杉磯則與以色列特拉維夫並列第十位。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現，美國城市在公共設施及家居傭工方面的成本最高；而在歐洲，主要是因為家庭、個人護理、休閒和娛樂費用高昂而推高生活費。<br />\n<br />\n根據調查，全球最低生活費的城市主要來自昰政治動盪或經濟出問題的國家。委內瑞拉經濟崩潰又出現超級通脹，首都加拉加斯（Caracas）取代陷入戰亂的敍利亞大馬士革排榜末。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡<br />\n<br />\n英國經濟學人智庫（EIU）全球生活費最貴十大城市：<br />\n1.新加坡<br />\n1.巴黎<br />\n1.香港<br />\n4.蘇黎世<br />\n5.日內瓦<br />\n5.大阪<br />\n7.首爾<br />\n7.哥本哈根<br />\n7.紐約<br />\n10.特拉維夫<br />\n10.洛杉磯"},{"pid":"cef23bf0d3e4a3cd1993328f92a51dbd159d3bfa","tid":1067984,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190319/59384557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190319%2F59384557&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b6fbe204\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190319%2F59384557&h=7ce46f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190319/59384557</a>"},{"pid":"640a71b26f36c8095b7fff3fee9b251f99b87cd7","tid":1067984,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"東京？"},{"pid":"aeffc412dc3c41e2e4b8d5fcc44b5a0e24c9b0f5","tid":1067984,"uid":73340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e861378ca2197311771218103bdbeb268566ece","tid":1067984,"uid":43133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:34:07.000Z","msg":"世界第一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n倫敦東京影都唔見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8eb1531d3428bd05bae6190cd162a6e89d7b0ee","tid":1067984,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeffc412dc3c41e2e4b8d5fcc44b5a0e24c9b0f5","tid":1067984,"uid":73340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"香港世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}